OL,3,CWrong family informed after prison
OL,4,Cinmate takes his own life
OL,6,FThe Prison Service has apologised
OL,7,Fafter the wrong family was informed
OL,8,Fwhen an inmate at a County Durham jail
OL,9,Ftook his own life.
OL,11,FThe error has emerged as part of the
OL,12,FPrisons and Probation Ombudsman's
OL,13,Finvestigation into the death of
OL,14,FMohammed Ahmed at HMP Frankland in
OL,15,FMarch 2024.
OL,17,FAhmed, who was serving an indefinite
OL,18,Fsentence having attempted to murder
OL,19,Fhis wife and later attacking a
OL,20,Fprobation officer, was found dead in
OL,21,Fhis cell.
