OL,3,CWrong family informed after prison
OL,4,Cinmate takes his own life
OL,6,FThe 46-year-old had served 10 years at
OL,7,FFrankland jail and did not phone his
OL,8,Ffamily.
OL,10,FThe PPO report stated that after his
OL,11,Fdeath, a family liaison officer was
OL,12,Fappointed and she tried to check next
OL,13,Fof kin details against the last family
OL,14,Fvisit Ahmed had received in 2023.
OL,16,FPolice in Rochdale, Greater
OL,17,FManchester, were sent to what was
OL,18,Fbelieved to be his next of kin's
OL,19,Faddress at around 4pm on 13 March
OL,20,F2024, after his death was confirmed at
OL,21,Fabout 6.30am that day.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
