OL,4,Cinmate takes his own life
OL,6,FThe report explained: "However,
OL,7,FRochdale police reported that it was
OL,8,Fnot the correct address for Mr Ahmed's
OL,9,Fnext of kin (and was in fact the
OL,10,Faddress of the next of kin of a
OL,11,Fdifferent prisoner at another prison)."
OL,13,FIt also said: "The initial details
OL,14,Fobtained for Mr Ahmed's next of kin
OL,15,Fwere taken from a visits list and
OL,16,Fwere, in fact, incorrect and for
OL,17,Fanother prisoner of the same name.
OL,19,F"This should not have happened."
