OL,6,FAhmed's real family were eventually
OL,7,Fcontacted the following day, at around
OL,8,F1pm.
OL,10,FThe Prison Service issued an apology
OL,11,Ffor the error and said inmates' next-
OL,12,Fof-kin details will be updated more
OL,13,Fregularly.
OL,15,FIt said: "We are very sorry for the
OL,16,Fdistress caused and have written to
OL,17,Fthe family concerned.
