OL,6,F"This error was quickly identified and
OL,7,Fcorrected, and steps have been taken
OL,8,Fto prevent this happening again
OL,9,Fincluding annual checks of next of kin
OL,10,Fdetails."
OL,12,FThe PPO report found that Ahmed had
OL,13,Fgiven no indication of having suicidal
OL,14,Fthoughts and that he had been referred
OL,15,Fto mental health services but had not
OL,16,Fengaged in the year before his death.
